snippet.title: Beer Ranger Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/790960/Beer_Ranger/

Logic platformer in the Oldschool style. The dwarfs are on a quest to find as much beer as they can. Only smart mind and skilfull hands will bring them to the desired goal. Will you manage to beat the most hardcore levels?
